<br>
Doing this is something to do while you are camping the AC otherwise its just not worth it unless you have your epic and a manastone.  If you do and you're in this level range than you'll see it is one of the better spots around.  Without it the downtime just makes the exp intake vs. med time ratio worse than Cynd or even soloing frogs in lguk. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=33635">Marcin Sanitee</a><br>
